<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 8:05AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Areas of Dense Fog this morning...
Areas of fog, dense in some locations, will persist through 10 AM
EST generally along and south of a Marion Indiana to Bluffton to
Ottawa Ohio line. Motorists will encounter areas of visibility
under one quarter mile at times this morning. Drivers should use
their low beam headlights to be seen by others, and be alert for
changing conditions. Slow down, and leave plenty of distance ahead
of you.</description>
